                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for S Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/bd151ab7-e941-4898-8bd1-3e9dabddcc5e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/bd151ab7-e941-4898-8bd1-3e9dabddcc5e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/98620&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/98620&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.15.1.el8_8.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/98620&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/98620&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.15.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can see the following error at the end of the test suite:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Starting ost4: -o localrecov  /dev/mapper/ost4_flakey /mnt/lustre-ost4
CMD: onyx-45vm8 mkdir -p /mnt/lustre-ost4; mount -t lustre -o localrecov  /dev/mapper/ost4_flakey /mnt/lustre-ost4
onyx-45vm8: mount.lustre: mount /dev/mapper/ost4_flakey at /mnt/lustre-ost4 failed: Address already in use
onyx-45vm8: The target service&apos;s index is already in use. (/dev/mapper/ost4_flakey)
pdsh@onyx-71vm1: onyx-45vm8: ssh exited with exit code 98
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
